Sentencas: Metal-supported solid oxide fuel cells (SOFCs) containing porous 430L stainless steel support, Ni-YSZ anode and YSZ electrolyte were fabricated by tape casting, laminating and co-firing in a reduced atmosphere.
Titulo: Metal-supported solid oxide fuel cells with in-situ sintered (Bi2O3)0.7(Er2O3)0.3-Ag composite cathode

Sentencas: (Bi2O3)(0.7)(Er2O3)(0.3)-Ag composite cathode was applied by screen printing and in-situ sintering.
Titulo: Metal-supported solid oxide fuel cells with in-situ sintered (Bi2O3)0.7(Er2O3)0.3-Ag composite cathode

Sentencas: The polarization resistances of the composite cathode were 1.18, 0.48, 0.18, 0.09 Omega cm(2) at 600, 650, 700 and 750 degrees C, respectively.
Titulo: Metal-supported solid oxide fuel cells with in-situ sintered (Bi2O3)0.7(Er2O3)0.3-Ag composite cathode

Sentencas: A promissing maximum power density of 568 mW cm(-2) at 750 degrees C was obtained of the single cell.
Titulo: Metal-supported solid oxide fuel cells with in-situ sintered (Bi2O3)0.7(Er2O3)0.3-Ag composite cathode

Sentencas: Short-term stability was measured as well.
Titulo: Metal-supported solid oxide fuel cells with in-situ sintered (Bi2O3)0.7(Er2O3)0.3-Ag composite cathode
